<Page
  title="Privacy · Lite Metal Industries"
  description="How Lite Metal Industries handles the details you send through this website."
  path="/privacy/"
  heading="Privacy"
  updated="June 2026"
>
  <p>
    This site is a brochure for Lite Metal Industries. It does not run accounts,
    advertising or visitor tracking.
  </p>

  <h2>The contact form</h2>
  <p>
    The enquiry form opens your own email app with the details you typed and
    sends them to us directly. Nothing you enter is stored on this website.
  </p>

  <h2>When you contact us</h2>
  <p>
    When you email or call, we keep what you send only to reply, prepare a quote
    and carry out the work. We do not sell or pass your details to anyone else.
    To have your email removed from our records, write to
    <a href="mailto:vishaldalmia@ymail.com">vishaldalmia@ymail.com</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Hosting</h2>
  <p>
    The site is served by a third-party host that may keep standard server logs,
    such as the date of a request and a general location, for security and
    reliability.
  </p>
</Page>
